</comment>
                            <comment id="15230454" author="nickmbailey" created="Thu, 7 Apr 2016 15:54:30 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Yeah a quick test with nodetool from 2.1 appears to be working with this patch.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15231162" author="yukim" created="Thu, 7 Apr 2016 21:54:00 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Overall looks good, but in 2.2 you cannot use java 8 feature like &lt;tt&gt;Optional&lt;/tt&gt; yet. 3.0+ it&apos;s fine.&lt;br/&gt;
That&apos;s why your dtest is failing on 2.2.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Can you create different patch for that?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15231166" author="yukim" created="Thu, 7 Apr 2016 21:57:14 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Created &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-11530&quot; title=&quot;Remove deprecated repair method in 4.0&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-11530&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-11530&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; for removing deprecated.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15232405" author="pauloricardomg" created="Fri, 8 Apr 2016 16:12:36 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks, updated 2.2 patch to use &lt;tt&gt;com.google.common.base.Optional&lt;/tt&gt; instead and resubmitted 2.2 tests.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15235454" author="yukim" created="Mon, 11 Apr 2016 16:43:06 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Update and test look good.&lt;br/&gt;
Committed as &lt;tt&gt;3557d2e05c8d1059562de2a91c1b33b4fcfcc6eb&lt;/tt&gt;.&lt;br/&gt;
Thanks!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
